<p itemprop="description"><b>创作立场声明：</b>在2020年末的时候终于得到了值得买定制手表礼盒，还有键帽，可谓圆满。先来晒一下手表吧，因为键帽还在路上。</p><p itemprop="description">在今年的<a href="https://post.smzdm.com/p/ar0n28q7/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">#双十一购物攻略#</a>活动中，得到张大妈的青睐，幸运地拿到了<strong>“卡西欧联名手表”</strong>奖励，特特拿出来晒一下。<img alt="“值”字当头鸿运来，卡西欧CASIO联名款定制礼盒（DW5600+剑玉）开箱晒单" src="https://res.smzdm.com/images/emotions/38.png" class="face" /> <br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a4wog2qx/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img alt="“值”字当头鸿运来，卡西欧CASIO联名款定制礼盒（DW5600+剑玉）开箱晒单" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202012/13/5fd5e7822ed845711.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">CASIO卡西欧很喜欢跟一些品牌跨界联名，比如NASA、本田、<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/13/" data-brandid="13" target="_blank">可口可乐</a>、高达、<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/2329/" data-brandid="2329" target="_blank">变形金刚</a>、复联、海贼王、七龙珠、<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/4081/" data-brandid="4081" target="_blank">哈根达斯</a>……</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a4wog2qx/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img alt="“值”字当头鸿运来，卡西欧CASIO联名款定制礼盒（DW5600+剑玉）开箱晒单" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/13/5fd5edb79e8b53892.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">这次就跟我们熟悉的张大妈合作推出了联名款礼盒，内含G-SHOCK小方块一只和什么值得买剑玉一个，小方块的型号是DW-5600HR-1PRZDM。 同款在京东的卡西欧店有售，定价690元。</p><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2804316"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="“值”字当头鸿运来，卡西欧CASIO联名款定制礼盒（DW5600+剑玉）开箱晒单" class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/13/5fd5ee8a8e5298257.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info  res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">卡西欧（CASIO）X什么值得买限定礼盒手表运动男表石英手表DW-5600HR-1PRZDM200米防水<strong class="price res_smzdm">690元</strong></span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">京东</span><